## Staff Claim Types

There are **FIVE (5) types** of staff claims. Please specify the nature of your claim in the "Staff Claim Type" field:

### 1. Employee Benefit

**Applicable For:**
- Dental claims
- Optical claims
- Health Screening claims only

**Requirements:**
- Clear image of receipt(s)/invoice(s) with your name
- Approval from authorised person

---

### 2. Travel Reimbursement

**Applicable For:**
- Travel expenses
- Parking
- Taxi
- Mileage

**Requirements:**
- Clear image of receipt(s)/invoice(s)
- Approval from authorised person
- **e-Invoice required** (Malaysia staff only - see E-Invoicing section below)

---

### 3. Educational Assistance/Training

**Applicable For:**
- Educational Assistance
- Udemy Course
- Other educational programs

**Requirements:**
- **Approval from Talent Development Team** (MANDATORY)
- Any related invoices
- Certificate of completion
- **e-Invoice required** (Malaysia staff only - see E-Invoicing section below)

---',
